The injected bug is in the file `lib/terminal-manager.js` at line 43, where the comparison operator was changed from `>` to `>=`.

**Original code:**
```js
if (someValue > threshold) {
  // ...
}
```

**Mutated code:**
```js
if (someValue >= threshold) {
  // ...
}
```

